  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: The primary experimental dataset used to anchor hemolysis model inputs carries a dataVintage of 2025-10-15, predating the model revision of 2026-01-20. Re-validation against the revised model build is planned but not yet completed.",
