      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2) is under version control and a regression test suite is maintained. However, the January 2026 model revision introducing updated near-wall turbulence treatment was not accompanied by a full re-execution of the hemolysis-specific test suite prior to submission. Achieved level 3 rather than required level 4."
    },
