      "rationale": "Relative error on MIH ranges from 8% to 22% across 5 operating points. Experimental measurement uncertainty is propagated but model prediction uncertainty intervals are derived from Monte Carlo on pre-revision input distributions. No formal hypothesis test is applied. Achieved level 3."
