      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence to residual < 1e-6 for all equations; floating-point round-off assessed via double-precision sensitivity study.",
      "rationale": "Residuals converge to 1e-5 for continuity and momentum; hemolysis scalar residual stalls at 5e-5 at two operating points. Double-precision computation is confirmed but no round-off sensitivity study is documented. Achieved level 2."
    },
