      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum n=5 independent experimental replicates per operating point; statistical outlier analysis documented.",
      "rationale": "Three replicates were performed at each of the 5 operating points. This falls below the required minimum of 5 replicates for MRL 5 statistical confidence. No formal outlier analysis is documented. Achieved level 2."
