      "rationale": "A boundary condition equivalency table is provided mapping experimental to COU conditions. Rotational speed and flow rate are matched within 2%. Blood rheology differs between bovine (validation) and human (COU) blood; a viscosity correction factor is applied but its effect on hemolysis prediction is not formally quantified via sensitivity analysis. Achieved level 2."
